228
00:21:00,009 --> 00:21:01,636
It's so cool!

229
00:21:05,181 --> 00:21:08,184
This part here.
Shibuya buildings.

230
00:21:08,351 --> 00:21:09,394
Really pretty.

231
00:21:09,519 --> 00:21:11,396
I know that. The new...

232
