The new building!

233
00:21:13,731 --> 00:21:16,567
Totally different colors.
Each one.

234
00:21:19,070 --> 00:21:20,488
So cool...

235
00:21:20,989 --> 00:21:22,365
Hey Yatora.

236
00:21:26,035 --> 00:21:27,662
What's with that look?

237
00:21:28,621 --> 00:21:30,415
What?!

238
00:21:30,707 --> 00:21:33,042
