242
00:21:42,218 --> 00:21:46,305
Marking the direction of gravity
on this chart

243
00:21:47,223 --> 00:21:51,894
will show you that
the direction of force is different.

244
00:21:52,353 --> 00:21:54,313
You see, don't you?

245
00:21:54,856 --> 00:21:56,149
You follow me?

246
00:21:56,315 --> 00:21:58,317
So, Exercise 1.

